# NOTE: Dokploy's stored env (panel/DB) is the SOURCE OF TRUTH for prod — it
# rewrites this file from the panel value on every deploy. Editing tags here
# alone does NOT change prod.
#
# Prod deploy model (2026-06-30): version-tagged via Dokploy API. On each tag,
# release.yml calls compose.update to set TINYRAVEN_TAG/SITE_TAG to the release
# version (a new image ref forces Dokploy to pull the new digest — :latest got
# served from cache and never updated), then compose.deploy. These values mirror
# the panel for local `docker compose` use.
TINYRAVEN_TAG=v0.3.1
SITE_TAG=v0.3.1
